      "blocked_reason": "STRUMPACK requires Fortran source files (src/dense/lapack/*.f compiled into libstrumpack). On this Windows host, no MSVC-ABI Fortran compiler exists: MinGW gfortran (Strawberry) is MinGW-ABI and CMake refuses to mix it with MSVC-ABI Clang/HIP; TheRock's flang.exe is the internal LLVM Fortran frontend binary (not a user-facing driver) and cannot compile .f90 files; no Intel ifort/ifx installed. All-MinGW toolchain (gcc+gfortran) is blocked by CMake's 'Windows-Clang-HIP.cmake: mixes Clang and MSVC or GNU'. All-MSVC + gfortran Fortran is blocked by CMake passing MSVC linker flags to gfortran's ld. Unblocked by: install Intel oneAPI Fortran Compiler (ifort/ifx) or install a working LLVM flang driver (flang-new) for Windows MSVC-ABI.",
